posts.title: My First One
posts.text: 今天正好是我的生日，正好昨晚萌生出搞一个博客的想法，而且我妹今早提醒我，我才知道是我的生日，那第一篇文章，就祝自己：身体健康，要快快快乐乐乐滴！！！！ Quick StartCreate a new post1$ hexo new "My New Post" More info: Writing Run server1$ hexo server More info: Server Generate static files1$ hexo generate More info: Generating Deploy to remote sites1$ hexo deploy More info: Deployment
